Fred Thomson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Thomson 0 Not to be confused for a silent film director Frederick A. Thomson(1869-1925)
Frederick Clifton Thomson (February 26, 1890 – December 25, 1928) was an American silent film cowboy who rivaled Tom Mix in popularity before dying at age 38 of tetanus.
